    "name": "DELIVERY KORE",
    "steam_appid": 2295290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/105449aae00f142add3ebe7024152d8c.avif?t=1734593560\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在中间界的森林——埃勒乌西斯展开奇幻冒险！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到灵魂聚集、等待转生的神秘森林——埃勒乌西斯。化身森林少女科雷，探索埃勒乌西斯，拯救森林免受黑暗之雨的侵袭吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ 自由探索奇幻森林</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开放世界中尽情体验森林冒险的魅力！收集花朵、树木、动物等各种资源，揭开森林的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ 光与暗的对决</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着森林的主人妈妈倒下，黑暗之雨降临埃勒乌西斯，黑暗影子正在污染森林。科雷和波利将踏上净化森林、拯救妈妈的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>◻ 可爱的伙伴波利</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >波利不仅是冒险的伴侣，也是改变森林命运的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ 用光之石开启神秘传送门</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用光之石激活散布在森林各地的传送门，快速移动，提高冒险效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◻ <strong>打造属于你的科雷</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各种发型和服装，装扮成你理想中的科雷。找到异世界商人，还可以自定义颜色！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ 美少女角色生成系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用Stable Diffusion技术，用科雷收集的灵魂诞生新生命。实时生成的可爱、美丽的科雷样美少女等你来发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ 推荐给以下玩家</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      • 喜欢可爱角色和美少女收集的玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 享受开放世界自由玩法的玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 想要同时体验治愈与采集乐趣的玩家 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 追求深度剧情的单人游戏玩家  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就下载，化身森林中的快递员科雷，改变埃勒乌西斯的命运吧！守护森林，重拾光明的旅程即将开始！</p>",
